      "stem_html": "Draw a line-bond structure for propene, CH<sub>3</sub>CH<span data-math=\"\\text{=}\"></span>CH<sub>2</sub>. Indicate the hybridization of the orbitals on each carbon, and predict the value of each bond angle.",
